org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.individuals

Class SearchItemIndividual

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.individuals.Individual
      • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.individuals.ArrayIndividual
        • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.individuals.MultiobjectiveIndividual
          • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.individuals.SearchItemIndividual
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, ICloneable

    public class SearchItemIndividual
extends MultiobjectiveIndividual
    Represents an individual as an array of SearchItem objects. Can be used to search the parameters of machine-learning methods (computational agents). Each individual has a schema, which describes the possible values on each position, and it also has the particular value for each position.
    Author:
    Martin Pilat
